---
title: Pear & Choc-Chip Crumble with Whipped Cream & Flaked Almonds | Serves 4
description: We couldn’t think of a better way to finish off dinner than with this combination of juicy pear, rich dark chocolate chips and
an earthy crumble topping, all baked to sweet perfection. Don’t attempt to fight this temptation, because you may not win.
